{"lastModified":1774519854090,"uri":"c::10923570597::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Komodo National Park: Labuan Bajo, NTT (Summer) & Raja Ampat National Park: Sorong, West Papua (Winter)\n \nOperating Area: Bali, Lombok, Sumbawa, Sumba, Flores, Alor, Timor (Summer) & Ambon, Banda, Halmahera, Ternate, West Papua, Raja Ampat, Kaimana, Biak, Wakatobi (Winter).\nPlease kindly find our signature itineraries in the attachment section.\n\nEmbark on the journey of a lifetime through Indonesia's mesmerizing waters aboard this majestic phinisi yacht. This vessel elegantly blends traditional craftsmanship with modern luxury, featuring opulent cabins, spacious decks, and gourmet dining. Enjoy panoramic views, relax on the sun deck, and savor exquisite meals prepared by expert chefs using fresh, locally-sourced ingredients. Beyond luxurious comforts, the yacht offers unparalleled adventures amidst Indonesia’s natural wonders. Dive into vibrant marine life, explore hidden coves and pristine beaches, and trek through lush landscapes. Discover the biodiversity of Raja Ampat, swim with manta rays, and encounter Komodo dragons in their natural habitat. Each day brings new experiences, making this journey an unforgettable voyage through the enchanting Indonesian archipelago.","blueprint":{"name":"SANCTUARY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::4c2bec90-bdfc-11ef-b346-8978585c2c4e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::4c07c2c0-bdfc-11ef-b346-8978585c2c4e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::6b099e30-bdfe-11ef-97eb-e9932d26afea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::6b2e1620-bdfe-11ef-97eb-e9932d26afea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::18ebe080-bdfa-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::